column5: Fished lake Erie this morning, NY waters...It was abit rough but we managed a few nice ones!
nice fish that second one is a hog WTG!
damn....for some reason i cant see the pics, just a red cross in a white box, oh well....nice red crosses you got there.
Nice smallie! All these early season smallie reports from the USA has got me itchin for opener!
WTG Dax, that's a real beaut !!  Hopefully Lady Luck sticks with ya once the slimey season arrives in 2 weeks
Great report and pics!!!  ... noice fish, for a Bass  I just can't see targeting those nasty ol' disgusting ol' Bass when there are Pike that need to be caught!!!  Bring on the Pike Porn!!!
Nice work Dax - almost Musky time.......
